=== TASK DESCRIPTION ===
Build comprehensive integration tests that validate the full system works end-to-end: server + worker + real Git operations + workflow execution. These tests are the final validation that all components work together.

=== APPROACH ===
Created integration tests within the server crate at `crates/server/tests/integration.rs` to leverage existing migration infrastructure (`sqlx::migrate!("./migrations")`). Tests use `tower::ServiceExt::oneshot` to exercise the full Axum router without needing a real HTTP listener — this is the same proven pattern used by the existing server tests.

Also created a mock agent CLI script at `tests/mock_agent.sh` for future use by worker-level e2e tests.

