=== TECH STACK (from docs/TECH_STACK.md) ===

| Component | Stack |
|-----------|-------|
| Control plane | Rust (axum, tokio, sqlx), REST + SSE, PostgreSQL |
| Workers | Rust (tokio, reqwest, git2); agent via Claude Code or Cursor CLI (BYOL) |
| CLI | Rust (clap), SSE for tail and attach |
| Web UI | React + TypeScript, Vite, TanStack Query, SSE |
| Logging | JSON; dual-write (local files + central DB); SSE for tail |
| Auth | API key (CLI, Web, workers); TLS for all connections |

=== MIGRATION SCHEMA ===

Tables: api_keys (UUID pk), identities (TEXT pk), personas (UUID pk), workers (TEXT pk), sessions (UUID pk), jobs (UUID pk, FK→sessions, FK→workers), logs (UUID pk, FK→sessions, FK→jobs)

Key indexes: logs(session_id, timestamp), logs(job_id, timestamp), jobs(session_id), jobs(status), jobs(worker_id, status), workers(last_seen_at), sessions(status, created_at)

